WEBVTT

00:01.228 --> 00:04.096
I love you.

00:04.199 --> 00:05.325
<i>Previously on Scandal...</i>

00:05.433 --> 00:06.525
They're talking about you, Amanda.

00:06.635 --> 00:08.432
Everyone's gonna be talking about you.

00:08.536 --> 00:10.835
I never dreamed
I'd be listening to a tape of you

00:10.940 --> 00:12.373
moaning with a White House aide.

00:12.508 --> 00:13.806
Amanda Tanner is blackmailing you.

00:13.943 --> 00:16.207
Which means that
Olivia Pope is blackmailing you.

00:16.312 --> 00:17.974
I need to know
if you have any proof

00:18.081 --> 00:19.674
of what went on
with you and the President.

00:20.118 --> 00:21.244
I'm pregnant.

