who sounds vaguely like me.

33:21.791 --> 33:24.351
There's no proof.
Nobody even takes that tape seriously

33:24.461 --> 33:25.450
without it being vouched for,

33:25.562 --> 33:27.462
which means our problem
is Amanda Tanner.

33:27.564 --> 33:29.031
And she's not our problem, she's a kid.

33:29.567 --> 33:32.195
Our real problem is Olivia Pope.

33:34.573 --> 33:37.838
- You realize...
- I got into this job to help people.

33:38.544 --> 33:39.842
To change this country for the better.

33:40.847 --> 33:45.285
I am the President
of the United States of America.

33:45.653 --> 33:47.018
It's time I acted like it.

33:48.423 --> 33:51.916
Thank you, Mr. President.

34:13.652 --> 34:17.054
General Florez!
General Florez, you need to reconsider.

34:21.196 --> 34:23.527
You know that the Hague Convention
guarantees that custody

34:23.630 --> 34:25.793
must be decided by the parents'
home country, right?

34:25.900 --> 34:27.163
- Right? Yes.
- Yes!

34:27.268 --> 34:28.463
I know. I know she's your wife.

34:28.571 --> 34:29.800
I know she's the mother of your children.

34:29.906 --> 34:33.637
And I know she seems weak now,
but she is smart.

34:33.744 --> 34:35.406
She is powerful.

34:35.513 --> 34:37.606
And smart, powerful women
like Carolina,

34:37.715 --> 34:39.706
they don't curl up and hide
when they've been wounded.

34:39.818 --> 34:41.114
They strike back.

34:41.219 --> 34:43.882
By writing memoirs
and appearing on talk shows,

34:43.989 --> 34:45.581
and at benefits and on red carpets,

34:45.692 --> 34:49.219
talking about women's rights
in the developing world.

34:49.329 --> 34:51.992
And how babies
were ripped from her arms

34:52.099 --> 34:54.033
by a ruthless dictator
who can't run a family,

34:54.135 --> 34:55.159
much less a country.

34:55.303 --> 34:57.430
And then one day, out of nowhere,

34:57.539 --> 35:00.634
she's not just the mother
of your children anymore.

35:00.743 --> 35:02.108
She's a hero.

35:02.211 --> 35:05.773
And people everywhere,
here, in your country,

35:05.883 --> 35:10.685
people love a hero, General.
People rise up and fight for a hero.

35:10.789 --> 35:12.689
And I will make it my personal mission

35:12.791 --> 35:15.022
that the rest of the world
is behind them when they do.

35:15.127 --> 35:17.527
So you need to tread
very carefully here,

35:17.630 --> 35:21.328
because what you do today
may determine your political survival.

35:21.434 --> 35:24.892
This woman can either be the mother
of your children

35:25.006 --> 35:28.442
or the face of your opposition.
Now which would you prefer?

36:22.374 --> 36:23.898
Okay, just one question.

36:24.009 --> 36:25.568
What happened to no lines
will be crossed here,

36:25.678 --> 36:27.612
no one will be harmed
in the making of this date?

36:28.114 --> 36:29.240
Oh. So this is a date.

36:31.485 --> 36:33.282
Okay. One question.

36:36.958 --> 36:38.619
Was Amanda Tanner
sleeping with the President?

36:42.398 --> 36:44.992
Don't you wish.
Now that would be a story.

36:52.510 --> 36:54.171
Hello.

36:54.279 --> 36:55.679
Dennis and Katherine Mahoney,

36:55.781 --> 36:57.544
emigrated from County Cork, Ireland,

36:57.650 --> 36:59.811
to Washington D.C.
In the summer of 1860,

36:59.919 --> 37:01.182
just in time for the Civil War.

37:01.288 --> 37:04.018
Started with nothing,
built an empire selling news in the front,

37:04.124 --> 37:06.889
and in 1973 their great-granddaughter
Margaret Mahoney

37:06.994 --> 37:10.624
sold her family newsstand chain
for $25 million.

37:10.766 --> 37:13.599
But she kept one for herself,
one to sell to one of her employees.

37:13.702 --> 37:16.263
Kiyong Kim, who had also
been working at Mahoney News

37:16.372 --> 37:18.670
since emigrating to Washington
from Busan, South Korea.

37:18.775 --> 37:21.040
Also with nothing.

37:21.912 --> 37:23.880
Kiyong Kim learned English
at that newsstand.

37:23.981 --> 37:25.745
He became a U.S. Citizen
at that newsstand.

37:25.850 --> 37:28.751
And eventually, he became
the owner of that newsstand,

37:28.853 --> 37:31.254
because Mahoney News is everything
that makes this country great.

37:31.357 --> 37:35.384
It would be a crime against the nation
to knock it down for greed and profit.

37:35.494 --> 37:38.259
Your boy Kiyong's got a news crew
showing up at 2:30 tomorrow

37:38.365 --> 37:39.332
for the 5:00 news

37:39.433 --> 37:41.834
<i>and an 800-word human interest story
in the D, C, Weekly,</i>

37:41.970 --> 37:44.370
which comes out Thursday.

