39:05.269 --> 39:10.333
Oh! No! I'm sorry.
I wasn't clear.

39:10.442 --> 39:12.877
This isn't my war.
You know who sent me here?

39:12.978 --> 39:14.775
The President of the United States
sent me here.

39:15.414 --> 39:18.816
To this office,
